==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unsecularize
<hw>Un*sec"u*lar*ize</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>secularize</ets>.]</ety> <def>To cause to become
not secular; to detach from secular things; to alienate from the
world.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unsecure</ent>⟦br⟧
